  • Classes in common used by common 
    Class Description
    IChatUser
    User for a ChatApp in a chat room
    ICmd2ModelAdapter
    Adapter that enables a command to display a GUI component on the user interface of a local system.
    Whenever a command to process an unknown message is received, the local system should immediately give an instance of this adapter to the received command to connect it into the local system.
